  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01599:9efeb39d3856]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01600:9e643362e6a1]]\n本质上也是矢量的合成。比如一质点同时参与三个同方向、同频率简谐振动：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01601:d356b0ba366c]]\n三者相隔 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01602:eafb8dff296f]]，矢量相加后正好为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01603:a6eaf1b0ba56]]。三个等长相量首尾相接，围成闭合三角形。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01604:ff2eb9e78880]]{center}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01605:01d92270825d]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01606:06b3847e1b6f]]{center}\n",
