  "read_only_context_before": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01586:7f81133dbde9]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01587:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n设相位为[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01588:5cc5f4637a5a]]，则\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01589:98bda9ba7a1f]]\n又要求 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01590:9e9d0ba07584]]，即 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01591:46243fbd5a42]]，所以取 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01592:4adfe9e78819]]。从初相 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01593:3dcab44583b8]] 到第一次满足条件的相位 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01594:581237800393]]，相位增加 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01595:77017ff02edc]]。角频率 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01596:26ad26b480e7]]，故 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01597:c5cf709bc04f]]。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01598:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}",
